Wait. Wait a minute. Wait.

52
00:05:13,167 --> 00:05:15,835
[ Panting ]

53
00:05:15,902 --> 00:05:20,706
Did you just tell me that
not only am I not going
on this trip,

54
00:05:20,774 --> 00:05:22,708
but that you're taking
another woman?

55
00:05:22,776 --> 00:05:27,680
Honey, she's not
just "another woman."
She's my wife.

56
00:05:27,747 --> 00:05:30,416
<i>[ Charlotte ]</i>
<i>We've moved 18 times.</i>

57
00:05:30,484 --> 00:05:34,287
<i>It gets easy</i>
<i>to read the signs.</i>

58
00:05:34,355 --> 00:05:37,756
♪ The lightning
of his terrible, swift sword ♪

59
00:05:37,824 --> 00:05:42,828
♪ His truth is marching on ♪

60
00:05:44,164 --> 00:05:47,933
♪ Glory, Glory ♪

61
00:05:48,002 --> 00:05:50,736
