62
00:05:53,173 --> 00:05:56,442
<i>[ Charlotte ]</i>
<i>I feel I've wasted</i>
<i>half my life in cars.</i>

63
00:05:56,510 --> 00:06:00,380
<i>I try to be charitable:</i>
<i>taking care of Kate</i>
<i>and not killing mother,</i>

64
00:06:00,447 --> 00:06:03,616
<i>But, I ask you,</i>
<i>who ever heard the word of god...</i>

65
00:06:03,683 --> 00:06:06,952
<i>going 70 miles an hour</i>
<i>on the interstate?</i>

66
00:06:16,163 --> 00:06:18,731
<i>[ TV Reporter ]</i>
<i>President Kennedy arrived</i>
<i>at Hyannis Port this afternoon,</i>

67
00:06:18,798 --> 00:06:20,733
<i>leaving the rigors</i>
<i>of Washington behind.</i>

68
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:24,137
<i>On hand to greet him</i>
<i>as the presidential helicopter</i>
<i>touched down were his daughter--</i>

69
00:06:28,975 --> 00:06:31,110
<i>[ Kate ]</i>
<i>I don't think he wanted</i>
<i>those gifts they gave him.</i>

70
00:06:31,178 --> 00:06:33,913
Frankenstein and birds?

71
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:37,250
[ Laughing ]
No, sweetheart.

72
00:06:37,317 --> 00:06:41,254
The three wise men
brought the baby Jesus
Frankincense and Myrrh.

73
00:06:41,321 --> 00:06:43,256
Oh.

74
00:06:43,323 --> 00:06:47,026
It's not that I don't know about these things.
I choose to believe something else.

75
00:06:47,093 --> 00:06:49,495
<i>I got an idea.</i>
<i>How about some fudge?</i>

76
00:06:49,563 --> 00:06:51,630
- Yeah.
<i>- Charlotte, you want to go make some fudge?</i>

77
00:06:51,698 --> 00:06:54,100
I can't do anything...

78
00:06:54,168 --> 00:06:57,370
until I have everything the way it was.

79
00:06:57,438 --> 00:07:00,639
The whole point of moving is so
that everything can be different.

80
00:07:00,707 --> 00:07:04,143
I don't like waking up
and not knowing where I am.

81
00:07:04,211 --> 00:07:06,712
Well, then I'll make you a little sign
for over your bed that says:

82
00:07:06,780 --> 00:07:10,216
"Good morning, Charlotte.
You are now in East Port.
Have a lovely day."

83
00:07:10,284 --> 00:07:12,718
Oklahoma was great.
I liked living there.

84
00:07:12,786 --> 00:07:15,354
I know.
And you'll love living here
when you get used to it.

85
00:07:15,422 --> 00:07:17,656
Yeah,
and when you get used to it,
we'll move...

86
00:07:17,724 --> 00:07:19,725
<i>and everything</i>
<i>will change again.</i>

87
00:07:19,793 --> 00:07:21,727
Life is change, Charlotte.
Death is...

88
00:07:21,795 --> 00:07:26,699
dwelling on the past or staying
in one place too long.

89
00:07:28,302 --> 00:07:31,070
<i>[ Mrs. Flax ]</i>
<i>Charlotte, remind me to get you a decent pair of shoes.</i>

90
00:07:31,138 --> 00:07:33,739
- I don't want any.
- Don't be ridiculous.

91
00:07:33,807 --> 00:07:37,076
- Every woman wants new shoes.
- But those are from him.

92
00:07:37,143 --> 00:07:39,712
<i> [ Mrs. Flax ]</i>
<i>"Him"? Oh, him.</i>

93
00:07:39,779 --> 00:07:43,483
Charlotte says he'll visit one day.
How will he know we're here?

94
00:07:43,550 --> 00:07:46,586
Charlotte, you know what?
The only thing you can rely on
about your father...

95
00:07:46,653 --> 00:07:50,089
is that he can't be relied on.

96
00:07:50,156 --> 00:07:52,258
<i>Right there.</i>
<i>Hold on, hold on.</i>

97
00:07:52,326 --> 00:07:55,261
<i>[ Charlotte ]</i>
<i>I only have one memory</i>
<i>of my father.</i>

98
00:07:55,329 --> 00:07:59,165
<i>At least,</i>
<i>I think it was my father.</i>

99
00:08:09,109 --> 00:08:12,278
<i> [ Man ]</i>
<i> Honey, it's an eclipse.</i>
<i> Put these on.</i>

100
00:08:12,346 --> 00:08:14,780
<i>[ Little Charlotte Giggling ]</i>

101
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:30,729
<i>[ Charlotte ]</i>
<i>One day he'll come back.</i>
<i>I just hope he can find us.</i>

102
00:08:30,797 --> 00:08:35,568
<i>Dear God, please don't</i>
<i>let us be leaving right away.</i>

103
00:08:35,636 --> 00:08:37,903
<i>Please let me stop lying</i>
<i>all the time.</i>

104
00:08:37,971 --> 00:08:40,573
<i>Please don't let me fall</i>
<i>crazy in love so much...</i>

105
00:08:40,641 --> 00:08:43,576
<i>and please let someone fall</i>
<i>crazy in love back.</i>

106
00:08:43,644 --> 00:08:46,579
<i>And please send me a sign.</i>

107
00:08:46,647 --> 00:08:49,081
<i>Amen.</i>
[ Sighs ]

108
00:08:49,149 --> 00:08:51,284
<i>♪ Come out here on the floor ♪</i>

109
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,321
<i>♪ Let's rock some more ♪</i>

110
00:08:56,490 --> 00:08:59,758
<i>♪ Come out here on the floor ♪</i>

111
00:08:59,826 --> 00:09:01,694
[ Man ]
- Hello there.
- Hello.

112
00:09:01,761 --> 00:09:04,029
<i>♪ Let's rock some more</i>
<i>  Yeah ♪</i>

113
00:09:04,097 --> 00:09:06,199
<i>♪ Now when you get out here ♪</i>

114
00:09:06,266 --> 00:09:08,601
<i>♪ Don't you have no fear ♪♪</i>

115
00:09:08,669 --> 00:09:12,037
[ Honks Horn ]
- Hey!
