<i>Let's move it, huh?</i>

118
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:20,546
<i>[ Mrs. Flax ]</i>
<i>"Experienced mechanic."</i>
<i>"Sheet metal worker."</i>

119
00:09:20,614 --> 00:09:22,781
