131
00:09:56,983 --> 00:10:01,987
<i>[ Car Approaching ]</i>

132
00:10:08,662 --> 00:10:12,798
<i>♪ Johnny Angel</i>
<i>  Johnny Angel</i>
<i>  Johnny Angel ♪</i>

