00:10:12,866 --> 00:10:16,769
<i>♪ Johnny Angel</i>
<i>  You're an angel to me ♪</i>

134
00:10:16,836 --> 00:10:18,771
Hi.

135
00:10:18,838 --> 00:10:21,874
I just wondered
if you got moved in all right.

136
00:10:21,942 --> 00:10:23,876
Yeah,
we got moved in fine.

137
00:10:23,944 --> 00:10:26,779
My name's Joe Peretti.

138
00:10:26,846 --> 00:10:29,115
I work up the hill.

139
00:10:29,183 --> 00:10:32,718
So if you need anything done,
Ma'am--

140
00:10:32,786 --> 00:10:35,688
"Ma'am"?
[ laughs ]

141
00:10:37,691 --> 00:10:40,793
Well, what exactly is up the hill,
Mr. Peretti?

142
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:44,163
<i>The convent.</i>
<i>Protectors of the blessed souls.</i>

143
00:10:44,231 --> 00:10:46,299
<i>[ Charlotte ]</i>
<i>This is a sign.</i>

144
00:10:46,366 --> 00:10:48,801
<i>Thank you, God.</i>
<i>This is a real sign.</i>

