150
00:11:03,984 --> 00:11:06,919
Okay. I'll take a look.
<i> [ Car Door Closes ]</i>

151
00:11:06,987 --> 00:11:11,424
<i>♪ Call me up for a date</i>
<i>  But I just sit and wait ♪</i>

152
00:11:11,492 --> 00:11:13,792
<i>♪ I'd rather concentrate ♪</i>

153
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:16,028
<i>♪ On Johnny Angel ♪</i>

154
00:11:16,096 --> 00:11:18,030
<i>♪ Because I love him ♪♪</i>

155
00:11:18,098 --> 00:11:21,167
So, Joe, how old
did you say you were?

156
00:11:25,339 --> 00:11:27,273
Twenty-six
and cute as a button.

157
00:11:27,341 --> 00:11:29,509
Too bad you're set
on being a nun.

158
00:11:32,012 --> 00:11:35,948
You know, Charlotte,
you might be old enough
for a boyfriend now.

159
00:11:36,016 --> 00:11:39,118
If I'm old enough,
maybe you're too old.

160
00:11:39,186 --> 00:11:42,688
Don't be ridiculous.
A real woman is never too old.

161
00:11:54,701 --> 00:12:00,406
<i>[ Distant Chattering ]</i>

162
00:12:00,474 --> 00:12:06,312
<i>[ Chattering Continues ]</i>

163
00:12:07,814 --> 00:12:11,250
